   Wong Sato, Akira A.; Llacsahuanga Salazar, Juana R., Natl Agr Univ La Molina, Fac Forestry Sci, Lima, Peru.
   Kato, Makoto, Kyoto Univ, Grad Sch Human \& Environm Studies, Kyoto, Japan.},
